item.description: I am in my final year of my BscIT Degree at Eduvos. I have a higher certificate in Software Engineering through the MLM course from CTI/Eduvos I have a strong interest in optimizing all of the ways I interact with my computer. When I’m not working, I enjoy watching movies, reading books, swimming, hiking, learning skills, 3D modelling, pixel art, attempting to make games with Godot, writing blogs and learning languages.
